RUMAH SAKIT UMUM SUGITANI
MASATSUGU YABE, URUSAN UMUM

53
00:07:16,311 --> 00:07:17,812
"Bagian Umum"?

54
00:07:18,438 --> 00:07:21,232
Panggil ambulans… tolong.

55
