Ada kamera dasbor?

70
00:08:21,292 --> 00:08:22,502
Mestinya kau pasang.

71
00:08:23,044 --> 00:08:25,505
Kekerasan di jalan sering terjadi.

72
00:08:29,217 --> 00:08:30,510
Tolonglah aku.

73
