01:42:49,789 --> 01:42:51,248
Di situlah kita berbeda.

1183
01:42:55,711 --> 01:42:56,712
Akira.

1184
01:43:14,188 --> 01:43:15,272
Lepaskan dia!

1185
01:43:15,356 --> 01:43:16,982
Lepaskan aku, Takeshi!

1186
01:43:18,067 --> 01:43:19,694
Akira, run!

1187
01:43:20,319 --> 01:43:21,319
Lari!

1188
01:43:33,332 --> 01:43:36,836
- Ayo, Takeshi! Hentikan!
- Akira!

1189
01:43:39,422 --> 01:43:40,673
Takeshi?

1190
01:43:45,344 --> 01:43:46,595
Kau ingat?

1191
01:43:55,813 --> 01:43:57,523
Aku tak bisa menyelamatkanmu.

1192
01:44:01,569 --> 01:44:03,028
Maafkan aku.

1193
01:44:16,625 --> 01:44:19,628
Kuharap kau bisa hidup normal lagi.

1194
01:44:24,175 --> 01:44:25,176
Akira.

1195
01:44:31,807 --> 01:44:33,017
Ya.

1196
01:46:17,371 --> 01:46:18,414
Kenmochi!

1197
01:46:26,046 --> 01:46:27,840
Toshiro! Jangan!

1198
01:46:34,889 --> 01:46:36,807
Kenmochi! Keluarlah dari sana!

1199
01:46:54,491 --> 01:46:55,618
Kenmochi!

1200
01:47:07,671 --> 01:47:09,715
Kau tak boleh masuk begitu saja!

1201
01:47:11,216 --> 01:47:13,552
Maaf. Saya tak bisa mencegah dia.

1202
01:47:13,636 --> 01:47:14,637
Tak apa-apa.

1203
01:47:24,563 --> 01:47:26,982
Toshiro. Ada apa lagi?

1204
01:47:28,984 --> 01:47:30,986
Kenapa kau mengarahkanku ke sana?

1205
01:47:32,363 --> 01:47:34,156
Kau tahu tentang pelacak itu.

1206
01:47:35,324 --> 01:47:37,201
Dibuang di rumah pasangan Toma.

1207
01:47:40,788 --> 01:47:41,789
Bagaimana…

1208
01:47:43,832 --> 01:47:44,959
menurut Anda?

1209
01:47:48,253 --> 01:47:53,092
Kau manfaatkan aku untuk jaga-jaga
jika tak bisa membunuh monster itu.

1210
01:47:57,721 --> 01:48:00,975
Kami sedang berusaha buktikan
Kenmochi pencuri otak itu.

1211
01:48:01,517 --> 01:48:04,728
Dia membunuh psikopat buatan lainnya

1212
01:48:05,270 --> 01:48:06,897
untuk menebus dosa-dosanya.

1213
01:48:10,651 --> 01:48:13,195
Kau membunuhnya lebih dulu.

1214
01:48:16,281 --> 01:48:17,324
Pak Ninomiya.

1215
01:48:18,617 --> 01:48:20,828
Anda juga korban pasangan Toma.

1216
01:48:22,621 --> 01:48:25,582
Anda mau hidup menanggung dosa orang lain?

1217
01:48:30,254 --> 01:48:31,296
Nona Toshiro.

1218
01:48:35,718 --> 01:48:39,263
Tak ada yang bisa mengelak
dari jati diri mereka.

1219
01:48:41,015 --> 01:48:44,643
Saya tak butuh alasan untuk hidup.

1220
01:48:57,364 --> 01:48:59,950
Maaf, saya harus menjawab telepon ini.

1221
01:49:10,252 --> 01:49:11,253
Pak Ninomiya.

1222
01:49:15,549 --> 01:49:17,593
Saya pasti akan menangkap Anda.

1223
01:49:21,722 --> 01:49:23,599
Jangan mati dahulu.

1224
01:49:34,902 --> 01:49:37,362
Apa maksudnya tak jadi operasi?

1225
01:49:39,156 --> 01:49:40,949
Dasar pembohong.

1226
01:50:23,659 --> 01:50:24,660
Kau sudah bangun.

1227
01:50:27,746 --> 01:50:28,997
Istirahatlah dahulu.

1228
01:50:32,334 --> 01:50:33,335
Akira.

1229
01:50:35,546 --> 01:50:36,547
Aku…

1230
01:50:52,437 --> 01:50:53,856
Semua sudah berakhir.

1231
01:50:57,818 --> 01:50:59,778
Nanti kuceritakan.

1232
01:51:12,666 --> 01:51:14,168
Aku membuatmu takut.

1233
01:51:16,253 --> 01:51:17,254
Maafkan aku.

1234
01:51:50,954 --> 01:51:52,748
Itu bukan hanya untuk ayahku.

1235
01:51:54,458 --> 01:51:57,002
Kau hanya ingin memanfaatkanku!

1236
01:51:58,462 --> 01:52:01,423
Kau tak peduli dengan perasaanku!

1237
01:52:02,883 --> 01:52:06,136
Aku tak akan memaafkanmu! Bagaimana bisa?

1238
01:52:52,557 --> 01:52:54,142
Kau membela diri.

1239
01:52:58,897 --> 01:53:00,023
Dengar.

1240
01:53:01,525 --> 01:53:03,235
Temui detektif wanita itu.

1241
01:53:14,037 --> 01:53:15,038
Akira?

1242
01:53:15,872 --> 01:53:16,872
Aku…

1243
01:53:18,458 --> 01:53:19,543
Pergilah.

1244
01:53:21,169 --> 01:53:22,212
Pergi!

1245
01:54:00,625 --> 01:54:03,128
Penebang Kayu Buruk Rupa…

1246
01:54:07,924 --> 01:54:09,426
punya…

1247
01:54:12,888 --> 01:54:14,264
banyak teman baru.

